 \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pennsylvania\"}, {\"begin\": 12038, \"end\": 12047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Priscilla_Presley\", \"score\": 0.9991145488514429, \"rank\": 0.0008553829946823648, \"text\": \"Priscilla\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Priscilla_Presley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Priscilla_Presley\"}, {\"begin\": 12129, \"end\": 12134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998414670988476, \"rank\": 0.00015855803774882438, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BETHLEHEM, Pa. -- Fans of a former Bethlehem Catholic and Lehigh University standout are again invited to a local pub to watch the wrestler compete at the Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 12137, \"to\": 12310, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12137, \"end\": 12146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"score\": 0.8559816973941277, \"rank\": 0.16824927792583855, \"text\": \"BETHLEHEM\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\"}, {\"begin\": 12172, \"end\": 12181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"score\": 0.8559816973941277, \"rank\": 0.16824927792583855, \"text\": \"Bethlehem\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\"}, {\"begin\": 12182, \"end\": 12190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.999989255838466, \"rank\": 5.8376254298531515e-06, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 12195, \"end\": 12201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_River\", \"score\": 0.9869599834742656, \"rank\": 0.012115693825149277, \"text\": \"Lehigh\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_River\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_River\"}, {\"begin\": 12304, \"end\": 12309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9998414670988476, \"rank\": 0.00015855803774882438, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A watch party is scheduled to start Friday at 12:30 p.m. at Sotto Santi Pizzeria Pub in south Bethlehem to cheer on Darian Cruz.\", \"from\": 12312, \"to\": 12440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12406, \"end\": 12415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"score\": 0.9962833549741489, \"rank\": 0.0037305100024972847, \"text\": \"Bethlehem\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bethlehem\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruz, representing his grandparents' native Puerto Rico, is scheduled to wrestle Aman Sehrawat of India around 1:15 p.m. for the bronze medal in the 57 kg division.\", \"from\": 12442, \"to\": 12606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12486, \"end\": 12497, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9418672272542767, \"rank\": 0.061087921938156015, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}, {\"begin\": 12523, \"end\": 12527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\", \"score\": 0.8459966551046626, \"rank\": 0.18173593206826877, \"text\": \"Aman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valinor\"}, {\"begin\": 12540