012 and 2013 and a NCAA Division I national title at Lehigh University in 2017.\", \"from\": 12956, \"to\": 13104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13078, \"end\": 13084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_University\", \"score\": 0.6905196449191559, \"rank\": 0.44779701997362376, \"text\": \"Lehigh\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lehigh_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Head Wrestling Coach at University of Pennsylvania Roger Reina announced the addition of Olympian Darian Cruz as an assistant coach on Thursday afternoon.\", \"from\": 13106, \"to\": 13260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13157, \"end\": 13168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Reina\", \"score\": 0.9999688755957097, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Reina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Reina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Reina\"}, {\"begin\": 13195, \"end\": 13203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999941967964917, \"rank\": 5.801104513321941e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get local Breaking News alerts sent directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 13266, \"to\": 13325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13276, \"end\": 13289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.202092867812804e-14, \"text\": \"Breaking News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Breaking_news\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Success!An email has been sent towith a link to confirm list signup.\", \"from\": 13327, \"to\": 13395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Error!There was an error processing your request.\", \"from\": 13397, \